
Execute capsim by typing:

../bin/capsim

The universe in this directory is codec.t .
It implements a mu-law PCM codec.

In graphical mode select codec from the list in the open item in the file
menu.

This toplogy also show hierarchical block. Move the cursor to the TxCodec
block and click the left button. A popup menu will appear. 
Select "Down One Level" by clicking the middle button. 

A new workspace with the blocks of the TxCodec block appears. To make this
workspace current, click the mouse in an empty area of the workspace.

The RxCodec block is also hierarchical.


To bring capsim up in text mode type:
../bin/capsim -b
load codec
run

Type quit to exit capsim.

